            |                                                 |
            +-------------------------------------------------+

 @{fg shine}Hotkey:@{fg text}       Enter  a  string  describing  the  key-sequence which should
               open/close the cdxNetLaunch command window.
               You'll  see  and  hear  a display beep if your input isn't a
               valid @{"commodities hotkey" LINK Info_CxKeys}.

 @{fg shine}Okay:@{fg text}         Accept the new values.
               Remember to select the @{i}Preferences/Save preferences @{ui}from the
               @{"command window" LINK UseCmdWin} menu to save your changes !

 @{fg shine}Undo:@{fg text}         Restore your old values.

